('64b62a1d7f714', '649345cf9eb60', '649346f34e3ba', '649347091aeee', 'None', 'An instance is launched into a VPC subnet with the network ACL configured to al low all inbound traffic and deny all outbound traffic. The instance\'s security group is configured to allow SSH from any IP address and deny all outbound traffic. What changes need to be made to allow SSH access to the instance? ', 'text', 'deo@cloudschool.com', '2023-07-18 05:58:53.522433', 'A'),
